data.description:
This charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath, all-brick ranch is move-in ready & close to everything in Charlotte! This home is perfect for first-time homebuyers, investors, or anyone looking for an affordable house in a great location.

This home has a new architectural roof & beautiful LVP floors. You’ll love the stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen & the high-quality LG washer & dryer. The granite countertops in the kitchen have plenty of counter space, ideal for cooking & meal prep. All 3 bedrooms are generously sized, & the bathroom has been updated with modern fixtures & finishes.

Imagine living in the heart of Charlotte with a huge fenced-in backyard that's perfect for grilling out & entertaining. There’s also additional parking behind the gate. You’ll be minutes from the rail line, Plaza Midwood, NoDa, & Uptown Charlotte. Offering seller concessions & loan is assumable if Buyer qualifies. Come experience living in a fantastic home in an amazing location.
